Package com.dao

package com.dao
This package includes classes for working with DB. One object of Dao class presents one DB table. Each dao class contains basic methods for carrying out transactions to the DB.

Classes in package:

  • UserDao - Dao class for User entity
  • CarDao - Dao class for Car entity
  • BookingDao - Dao class for Booking entity

Since:
1.0

    The BookingDao class provides methods for interacting with the "booking" table in the database.
